--- Node.js ---

Ignore all node_modules folders in frontend, backend, or anywhere else

**/node_modules

--- Secrets ---

Ignore all .env files and their variants.

These files contain your secret database passwords and API keys.

**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.development
**/.env.production
**/.env.*.local

Do NOT ignore the example file. This is safe to commit.

!**/.env.example

--- Logs ---

Ignore log files from npm, yarn, etc.

npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
*.log

--- Frontend (Vite/React) ---

Ignore the production build output folder

/frontend/dist

Ignore the Vite cache

/frontend/.vite/

Ignore ESLint cache

/frontend/.eslintcache

--- Backend (Node/Prisma) ---

Ignore the production build output folder

/backend/dist

